{"tid":2001182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首季GDP跌8.9%　為1974年有統計以來最大跌幅","createTime":"2020-05-04T11:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T12:04:47.000Z","uid":125193,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec2b9983dbec521166d3db217d633558f7c5dfb","tid":2001182,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">開心，高興</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情令香港經濟陷入衰退，政府公布今年第一季的本地生產總值(GDP)預先估計數字，較上年同期實質下跌8.9%；2019年第4季的跌幅為3.0%。<br />\n政府發言人指，今年首季的GDP預測跌幅，是自1974年第一季有紀錄以來最大的單季按年跌幅，主要由於新冠肺炎疫情的威脅對本地廣泛經濟活動，以及區內供應鏈構成嚴重干擾，導致香港的經濟衰退在上季加劇。隨着疫情在3月演變成全球大流行，對經濟影響變得更嚴重。<br />\n香港經濟各主要組成部分方面，貨物出口上季按年跌9.7%，比之前一季的2.5%跌幅進一步擴大，主因是區內供應鏈及相關貿易活動，在疫情威脅下受到嚴重干擾。上季服務輸出按年跌37.8%，為有紀錄以來最大的單季跌幅，部分反映了訪港旅遊業受到重挫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內部需求方面，上季私人消費開支的跌幅急劇擴大，按年下跌10.2%，主因是疫情下政府實施社交距離限制措施，嚴重干擾與消費相關活動，而勞工市場情況嚴峻，亦對消費情緒造成沉重打擊。在營商氣氛悲觀和建造活動疲弱下，整體投資開支續見大幅收縮，按年下跌13.9%。<br />\n政府發言人指，展望未來，隨着疫情全球大流行導致環球經濟活動嚴重萎縮，香港的出口短期內仍將顯著受壓，加上美國與內地經貿關係的發展、地緣政治緊張局勢及環球金融市場波動，亦須繼續關注。香港若疫情威脅持續，預料經濟活動短期內仍然欠佳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200504/mobile/bkn-20200504163009672-0504_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200504%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200504163009672-0504_00822_001.html&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1udgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=c6238fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200504/mobile/bkn-20200504163009672-0504_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"99c20d3163791ef085f13d8fda664a6a8c24b3fb","tid":2001182,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真。光復香港 時代革命 睇今次啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84744b8640b1ac4563e31f079534ee75e18565b9","tid":2001182,"uid":12267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99c20d3163791ef085f13d8fda664a6a8c24b3fb","tid":2001182,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真。光復香港 時代革命 睇今次啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"點解經濟差，就會光復到香港？"},{"pid":"b40eafcbdf3e49a8ebe1bc8ce5ea9c749c1068ad","tid":2001182,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"武肺果然係手足黎<br />\n<br />\n支持武肺手足依法攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce2d445ed7b82910c072a52dbfa165153cebc4d","tid":2001182,"uid":189138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:09:00.000Z","msg":"公務員係咪會減薪?"},{"pid":"06e5a7a014980186b6d780fc4c128431c9470c7a","tid":2001182,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0864c8719102fc4c07d6850ab1eddf7946e3c2cd","tid":2001182,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"藍資趺18%<br />\n<br />\n黃營升9%  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a2f7ce37c678cf3ed86a0acb045a894f1af21c","tid":2001182,"uid":54415,"